WEBVTT

00:01:28.032 --> 00:01:30.413
Agar gapiruvchi ushbu

00:01:30.413 --> 00:01:32.089
qarama-qarshi iboraga biroz

00:01:32.089 --> 00:01:35.294
zaharhandalik qo'shsa va kimgadir 
tegadigan yoki

00:01:35.294 --> 00:01:37.137
uning ustidan kuladigan qilib aytsa,

00:01:37.137 --> 00:01:38.797
bu unda sarkazm hisoblanadi.

00:01:38.797 --> 00:01:40.465
Mana yana bir misol:

00:01:40.465 --> 00:01:41.548
"Ajoyib ish!"

00:01:41.548 --> 00:01:43.954
Kimdir o'z orzusiga erishdi:

00:01:43.954 --> 00:01:44.748
zo'r!

00:01:44.748 --> 00:01:46.810
Kimdir chempionatda g'olib bo'ldi:

00:01:46.810 --> 00:01:47.667
ajoyib!

00:01:47.667 --> 00:01:50.047
Kimdir mashinaga urildi:

00:01:50.047 --> 00:01:52.724
yaxshi emas.

00:01:52.724 --> 00:01:56.441
Shuning uchun, yo'lovchi "ajoyib ish!" 
deganida, aslida

00:01:56.441 --> 00:01:57.969
u teskarisini nazarda tutib,

00:01:57.969 --> 00:02:00.191
biroz hazil ohangini beradi.